## Alternative: deploy everything with Docker Compose (your own VPS)

If you operate a single VM instead of Render + Vercel:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Fill all production values on the server
docker compose up -d --build
```

Expose **HTTPS** via Nginx/Caddy/`infra/nginx` and set **`CORS_ORIGINS`** / **`NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`** to your public URLs. See **`README.md`**.

---

## Alternative: frontend + API both on Vercel

Possible for lighter APIs; your Python stack may hit **bundle or timeout limits**. Steps: **`docs/vercel.md`**.

